rows.label: qst202212_0010
rows.name: It's all right. She won't shock you.

rows.label: qst202212_0040
rows.name:
Now...why don't you say thank you
to the nice lady?

rows.label: qst202212_0070
rows.name:
It's true!
You're not shocking me!

rows.label: qst202212_0080
rows.name:
That's great!
I'm not dead of the 'lectric!

rows.label: qst202212_0090
rows.name: Oh...haha, thank goodness I didn't electrocute you!

rows.label: qst202212_0110
rows.name:
Don't mention it...
I should thank you!

rows.label: qst202212_0120
rows.name:
It's only thanks to you that
I finally learned to love my powers.

rows.label: qst202212_0130
rows.name:
I feel like I'm all grown up now!
Well...a little bit, at least! Haha...
